item.title: Fish Task & API Integration (Yale School of Medicine)
item.description: Description The Fishing Task is a game developed in JavaScript and Node.JS, and modelled upon an original version in PsychoJS. Additionally, API integrations with external services were done using AWS Lamdba. Code: Purpose The Fishing Task is an online behavioral task developed for the Powers Lab at Yale Medical School to use on clinical and healthy populations during clinical studies on ketamine, a psychoactive used for pain relief, anxiety and mood disorders.
